Finally, please stop the car at the
edge of the cliff over there.

28
00:02:59,312 --> 00:03:02,515
Yes! Leave things to me!

29
00:03:02,515 --> 00:03:04,284
Hey, be quiet!

30
00:03:04,284 --> 00:03:06,616
You're not the driver!

31
00:03:07,320 --> 00:03:09,756
Oh, no, don't say such cruel things to me!

32
00:03:09,756 --> 00:03:12,316
Let's get intimate, all right?

33
00:03:17,230 --> 00:03:20,833
That jerk! He's out of control.

34
00:03:20,833 --> 00:03:22,335
Ready?

35
00:03:22,335 --> 00:03:24,428
All right, start!

36
00:03:32,145 --> 00:03:34,477
Finally, we're alone, just the two of us.

37
00:03:39,185 --> 00:03:41,921
Incredible! I feel as if we'll be blown up!

38
00:03:41,921 --> 00:03:42,855
You're right.


39
00:03:42,855 --> 00:03:45,847
If you don't want to die, you had
better not make a pass at me.

40
00:03:47,393 --> 00:03:48,826
Right...

41
00:03:57,103 --> 00:04:00,440
Aren't you driving a little too fast?

42
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,375
