150
00:11:55,548 --> 00:11:57,216
I guess they spend as much
money as they can

151
00:11:57,216 --> 00:11:59,351
so they can compete with American movies.

152
00:11:59,351 --> 00:12:03,219
Yes, so Yuki should do her best.


153
00:12:04,056 --> 00:12:06,217
Miss Yuki, good luck.

154
00:12:11,964 --> 00:12:14,366
