159
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:30,249
Mr. Saeba, where are we going?

160
00:12:30,249 --> 00:12:33,878
We came to the beach, so we have to swim.

161
00:12:34,420 --> 00:12:36,922
I brought a bathing suit for you of course!

162
00:12:36,922 --> 00:12:39,258
And of course it's a high-leg cut!

163
00:12:39,258 --> 00:12:40,225
Really!

164
00:12:43,229 --> 00:12:44,821
Ya-hoo!

165
00:12:44,997 --> 00:12:49,400
Feels so good! Yuki, hurry up
and come over here!

166
00:12:54,974 --> 00:12:57,977
I'm not in the mood for swimming.

167
00:12:57,977 --> 00:13:01,814
I can't believe that I was trying to kill myself.

168
00:13:01,814 --> 00:13:02,974
I...

169
00:13:05,084 --> 00:13:09,817
The hypnosis was why I thought I'd get
my memory back, wasn't it?

170
00:13:10,356 --> 00:13:14,656
So, what should I believe from now on,
and how can I live?

171
00:13:18,063 --> 00:13:21,931
I'm sure that the killer will
come for you today.

172
00:13:22,735 --> 00:13:26,603
But at the same time, it's the
best chance you'll have.

173
00:13:28,874 --> 00:13:32,745
He'll be able to remove the
block in your memory

174
00:13:32,745 --> 00:13:35,047
because he's the one who hypnotized you.

175
00:13:35,047 --> 00:13:38,117
So when he appears in front of you,

176
00:13:38,117 --> 00:13:40,347
it'll be time for you to get
your memory back.

177
00:13:41,053 --> 00:13:43,556
I promise you that I'll catch him.

178
00:13:43,556 --> 00:13:47,860
So the only thing you need to do
is to wait for him.

179
00:13:47,860 --> 00:13:49,895
I'm your bodyguard.

180
00:13:49,895 --> 00:13:54,059
I'll be there no matter what danger comes
to you, and I will protect you.

181
00:13:59,405 --> 00:14:02,238
Mr. Saeba, you're...

182
00:14:04,410 --> 00:14:06,912
Hey, what are you doing?

183
00:14:06,912 --> 00:14:10,149
That was mean! Why did you
do that all of a sudden?

184
00:14:10,149 --> 00:14:11,784
Take this, revenge!

185
00:14:11,784 --> 00:14:13,718
Hey, wait a second.

186
00:14:21,927 --> 00:14:23,724
Oh, no, I can't run any further.

187
00:14:26,599 --> 00:14:27,964
Mr. Saeba...

188
00:14:34,273 --> 00:14:36,675
What the hell is this?! Kaori?!

189
00:14:36,675 --> 00:14:40,839
See, Miss Yuki, it's easy to get him.

190
00:14:41,680 --> 00:14:43,415
Here, here!

191
00:14:43,415 --> 00:14:46,384
Kiss it, kiss it!

192
00:14:49,989 --> 00:14:54,085
Excuse me, but you're Miss Yuki Oikawa,
the stuntwoman, aren't you?

193
00:14:55,628 --> 00:14:57,425
Save me!

194
00:15:02,902 --> 00:15:03,926
Who is that?

195
00:15:04,637 --> 00:15:07,306
Maybe he's a television reporter?

196
00:15:07,306 --> 00:15:08,432
Strange...

197
00:15:10,209 --> 00:15:12,404
Who killed the robin?

198
00:15:17,082 --> 00:15:18,717
Are you all right, Yuki?

199
00:15:18,717 --> 00:15:20,184
Yes!

200
00:15:23,822 --> 00:15:24,757
Wait!

201
00:15:24,757 --> 00:15:26,019
Ryo!

202
00:15:26,692 --> 00:15:27,359
Ryo!

203
00:15:27,359 --> 00:15:28,826
Miss Yuki!

204
00:15:29,862 --> 00:15:31,124
Wait!

205
00:15:38,971 --> 00:15:40,472
Who asked you to do it?

206
00:15:40,472 --> 00:15:43,134
Prince Alapanas!

207
00:15:43,709 --> 00:15:45,477
Who the hell is he?

208
00:15:45,477 --> 00:15:47,446
The prince of Alinamia.

209
00:15:47,446 --> 00:15:49,815
Why does he want to kill Yuki?

210
00:15:49,815 --> 00:15:53,615
If she dies, Prince Alapanas will
become the next king.

211
00:15:53,819 --> 00:15:55,616
Then, Yuki is...

212
00:15:55,921 --> 00:16:00,085
Yes, she is Princess Yuki Grace of Alinamia.

213
00:16:07,800 --> 00:16:11,870
Even though I'm not with her,
the mind control still works.

214
00:16:11,870 --> 00:16:12,905
What?

215
00:16:12,905 --> 00:16:14,506
After she jumps into the sea,

216
00:16:14,506 --> 00:16:18,135
she won't be able to get back to the surface.

217
00:16:24,950 --> 00:16:28,253
It sounds like nagging, but let me
explain this again, Miss Yuki.

218
00:16:28,253 --> 00:16:29,755
Oh, yes, please.

219
00:16:29,755 --> 00:16:32,191
First of all, you turn the automatic
pilot on above the water.

220
00:16:32,191 --> 00:16:33,559
Then, the pilot will...

221
00:16:33,559 --> 00:16:35,584
What? Is something wrong?

222
00:16:38,931 --> 00:16:41,764
Who killed the robin?

223
00:16:42,434 --> 00:16:45,562
Now she's as good as dead.

224
00:16:50,342 --> 00:16:51,502
Idiot!

225
00:16:53,345 --> 00:16:56,178
Idiot, you can't win against me
without a weapon.

226
00:17:03,188 --> 00:17:05,918
Ten seconds until the explosion.

227
00:17:07,026 --> 00:17:10,763
Damn, I wonder where Ryo went?!

228
00:17:10,763 --> 00:17:12,097
Nine...

229
00:17:12,097 --> 00:17:13,766
Eight...

230
00:17:13,766 --> 00:17:15,134
Seven...

231
00:17:15,134 --> 00:17:16,702
Six...

232
00:17:16,702 --> 00:17:18,470
Five more seconds.

233
00:17:18,470 --> 00:17:19,805
Four...

234
00:17:19,805 --> 00:17:20,772
Three...

235
00:17:21,607 --> 00:17:22,631
Two...

236
00:17:23,509 --> 00:17:24,476
One...

237
00:17:25,477 --> 00:17:26,444
Zero!

238
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:37,353
Wow! Incredible! Wow!

239
00:17:40,692 --> 00:17:41,750
What?!

240
00:17:43,228 --> 00:17:44,563
What's going on?


241
00:17:44,563 --> 00:17:46,963
My hands, my legs...

242
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:51,470
Hey, she hasn't come to the surface yet.

243
00:17:51,470 --> 00:17:53,062
What's wrong with the stuntwoman?

244
00:17:53,505 --> 00:17:55,132
Something weird is happening.

245
00:17:55,541 --> 00:17:55,974
Is Yuki all right?

246
00:17:55,974 --> 00:17:58,944
What the hell are you standing around for?!
Where's the rescue boat?!
Is Yuki all right?

247
00:17:58,944 --> 00:18:00,138
What the hell are you standing around for?!
Where's the rescue boat?!

248
00:18:00,813 --> 00:18:03,008
Ryo... Where are you, Ryo?

249
00:18:03,482 --> 00:18:07,453
No matter what you do, your hands
and legs will be so numb

250
00:18:07,453 --> 00:18:11,184
that you'll sink to the bottom of the sea.

251
00:18:11,890 --> 00:18:13,721
Somebody...

252
00:18:14,426 --> 00:18:15,928
Ryo!

253
00:18:15,928 --> 00:18:16,986
Who's that?

254
00:18:24,670 --> 00:18:25,637
Ryo!

255
00:18:41,420 --> 00:18:43,217
Mr. Saeba!

256
00:19:02,241 --> 00:19:04,141
What are you saying?

257
00:19:05,644 --> 00:19:09,381
Miss Yuki is the Princess of Alinamia?

258
00:19:09,381 --> 00:19:14,045
Yes, Your Highness, you are the princess
of our country, Alinamia.

259
00:19:14,653 --> 00:19:16,021
Please feel at ease.

260
00:19:16,021 --> 00:19:20,592
In our country, Prince Alapanas has
already been deported.

261
00:19:20,592 --> 00:19:23,026
Really, there's nothing to worry about.

262
00:19:23,862 --> 00:19:25,898
It's a bad joke.

263
00:19:25,898 --> 00:19:29,368
Me, a princess?

264
00:19:29,368 --> 00:19:34,173
It's not a joke. Please do not worry
about your amnesia.

265
00:19:34,173 --> 00:19:37,843
A mind control specialist was called in
from our country and is already here.

266
00:19:37,843 --> 00:19:40,277
Your memory will be back soon.

267
00:19:43,515 --> 00:19:44,607
Princess?!

268
00:19:52,925 --> 00:19:53,892
Yuki!

269
00:20:02,568 --> 00:20:05,435
I... I don't know what to do now.

270
00:20:06,104 --> 00:20:08,937
I know I've been seeking my
memory for a long time,

271
00:20:09,474 --> 00:20:12,307
but now I don't care about my past.

272
00:20:13,045 --> 00:20:17,709
I've realized that there are more
important things to me.

273
00:20:18,951 --> 00:20:20,077
Mr. Saeba...

274
00:20:20,752 --> 00:20:23,722
I don't want to change anything anymore.

275
00:20:23,722 --> 00:20:26,122
I want to stay as I am now, forever.

276
00:20:35,801 --> 00:20:36,927
Here we are.

277
00:20:40,806 --> 00:20:41,773
This place...

278
00:20:51,583 --> 00:20:52,709
Mr. Saeba!

279
00:20:55,687 --> 00:21:02,616
I know that you've realized that this
is the only place you can go.

280
00:21:20,312 --> 00:21:23,008
Mr. Saeba, thank you.

281
00:21:25,284 --> 00:21:27,752
I'll ask someone to erase
my memories of you.

282
00:21:28,186 --> 00:21:31,644
Then I won't need to feel so sad.

283
00:21:33,425 --> 00:21:34,551
Yuki...

284
00:21:37,429 --> 00:21:38,919
Mr. Saeba!

285
00:21:42,801 --> 00:21:44,428
Goodbye...

286
00:21:55,747 --> 00:21:59,318
Wow, that's Princess Grace.
She's so beautiful!

287
00:21:59,318 --> 00:22:04,389
Yeah, I've heard that she's going back to her
country today for the coronation ceremony.

288
00:22:04,389 --> 00:22:06,482
Wow, how wonderful!

289
00:22:24,209 --> 00:22:26,011
I know that you restrained yourself.

290
00:22:26,011 --> 00:22:29,242
You silly, who are you talking about?

291
00:22:37,622 --> 00:22:43,288
If you're feeling, even though you
tend to your accessories

292
00:22:45,630 --> 00:22:50,192
You can't compete against the
rainbows and stars

293
00:22:53,405 --> 00:22:57,967
Tidings from the wind taught me

294
00:23:01,380 --> 00:23:07,785
Your smile is important,
all of my love forever

295
00:23:08,253 --> 00:23:14,214
Raise your downcast face
and look up at the sky

296
00:23:14,359 --> 00:23:21,265
Give me peace in my hands, starting over

297
00:23:23,568 --> 00:23:29,768
Smile and smile, you are the angel
on a shooting star

298
00:23:31,476 --> 00:23:35,845
Heart and heart, at this very moment

299
00:23:39,518 --> 00:23:45,753
Smile and smile, you are the angel
on a shooting star

300
00:23:47,392 --> 00:23:51,590
Heart and heart, at this very moment

301
00:23:55,434 --> 00:23:57,800
Smile and smile...

302
00:24:01,373 --> 00:24:04,042
Oh, I haven't told you about it, have I?

303
00:24:04,042 --> 00:24:06,169
I am a professional at helping
people escape.

304
00:24:11,249 --> 00:24:16,621
Therefore, the money he paid me with
was that of a desperate old man.

305
00:24:16,621 --> 00:24:18,589
I will help him escape, I swear it.

306
00:24:24,563 --> 00:24:30,524
With a Class A License for Love
Here She Is, a Beautiful Pro
at Helping People Escape

